# MLN deployment (rule)

- Follow **`.cursor/skills/mln-deployment/SKILL.md`** for Compose stacks, **`mlnd-release`**, Makefile image/binary targets, and env templates.
- **Never commit** real private keys, relay passwords, or Tor secrets — only **`.example`** files and documentation.
- After changing **defaults** (RPC, chain IDs, relay URLs), cross-check **`PHASE_16_PUBLIC_TESTNET.md`**, **`mln-cli/internal/config/settings.go`**, and **`README.md`** via **`.cursor/skills/doc-sync/SKILL.md`** when phase claims are affected.
- For **CI test behavior**, coordinate with **`.cursor/skills/mln-qa/SKILL.md`**.
